Package: DIFMagnitude
Title: DIF Magnitude Measurement Functions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Richard N", "Jones", 
           email = "rich_jones@brown.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functions for computing and analyzing Differential Item Functioning (DIF)
    magnitude measures for continuous, dichotomous, and ordered categorical items.
    The package takes advantage of Mplus output (e.g., H5 format) but is designed
    to be operationalizable with any latent variable modeling software.
